Alright, you go ahead.

263
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:17,540
Ce.

264
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:18,510
Lingyun.

265
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,780
Let's go to the courtyard and regroup with Jing and the others.

266
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:22,140
Let's make the necessary arrangements

267
00:21:22,140 --> 00:21:23,400
and be ready to provide support at any time

268
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,580
for these martial artists

269
00:21:24,580 --> 00:21:26,420
who have been demonized and left the Love and Desire Valley.

270
00:21:26,420 --> 00:21:27,080
-Yes!
-Yes.

271
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:27,840
Let's go.

272
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:35,120
As expected of the old man Fengyue's disciple.

273
00:21:35,690 --> 00:21:38,650
Such cultivation at such a young age.

274
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:41,310
It makes me appreciate your talent.

275
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:43,280
How about this?

276
00:21:44,020 --> 00:21:45,710
Why don't we join forces?

277
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:48,820
Just like Yeyuan and I did back then.

278
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:51,670
If we stand together,

279
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:53,460
not just in this mortal realm,

280
00:21:53,670 --> 00:21:55,640
but even dominating the three realms

281
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,100
would be within our reach.

282
00:21:57,470 --> 00:21:59,380
18 years ago, you and Demon Lord Yeyuan

283
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:01,110
failed to obtain the Millennium Token.

284
00:22:01,110 --> 00:22:03,370
After that, you retreated to Mount Suyu.

285
00:22:03,370 --> 00:22:05,340
I didn't expect that after 18 years,

286
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:07,740
your ambition would remain undiminished.

287
00:22:08,910 --> 00:22:10,240
Is it not possible

288
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:12,510
for a person to have some aspirations?

289
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:14,870
Are you sure you won't consider joining?

290
00:22:14,870 --> 00:22:17,500
Exorcising demons and protecting the righteous path is my lifelong mission, Mo Xiao.

291
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:18,960
It's engraved in my bones.

292
00:22:22,210 --> 00:22:24,810
Perhaps one day you'll realize.

293
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:27,800
I can rewrite your destiny.

294
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:30,380
Your evil deeds are piled high.

295
00:22:30,380 --> 00:22:32,500
You will ultimately reap what you sow.

296
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:36,140
They willingly let me control them.

297
00:22:37,250 --> 00:22:38,130
Just like

298
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:40,440
Feng Lixue.

299
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:42,950
Next

300
00:22:42,980 --> 00:22:44,100
and you too.

301
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,550
Then I'll destroy your Demon Stone.

302
00:22:46,670 --> 00:22:47,700
Your life is mine.

303
00:22:55,700 --> 00:22:56,410
Jing,

304
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,890
you were just poisoned earlier.

305
00:22:57,890 --> 00:22:59,130
The poison has been neutralized now.

306
00:22:59,130 --> 00:23:00,060
You're fine now.

307
00:23:01,190 --> 00:23:02,230
Brother,

308
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:04,070
I haven't done anything

309
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:06,430
shameful, have I?

310
00:23:07,030 --> 00:23:08,430
Of course not.

311
00:23:09,180 --> 00:23:09,920
Jing,

312
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:12,170
you should ask me about this.

313
00:23:12,190 --> 00:23:14,120
I could tell you a whole basketful.

314
00:23:16,290 --> 00:23:17,150
Father,

315
00:23:19,730 --> 00:23:20,860
I thought

316
00:23:20,890 --> 00:23:22,560
I would never see you again.

317
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:23,780
Don't talk nonsense.

318
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:26,930
I'll be relieved that you're alright.

319
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:28,720
I'm fine.

320
00:23:30,970 --> 00:23:31,780
Ce,

321
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,160
quickly use Fengyu Soundlink

322
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:35,250
to report the situation here back to Shushan Sect.

323
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:37,110
Let the Sect Leader be at ease too.

324
00:23:37,130 --> 00:23:38,130
Yes, father.

325
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,540
Where are the three Great Guardians?

326
00:23:46,530 --> 00:23:48,060
Greetings, Branch Leader.

327
00:23:50,540 --> 00:23:51,900
What happened to Zisu?

328
00:23:52,480 --> 00:23:53,000
She...

329
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:54,250
Don't just stand there, you two.

330
00:23:54,250 --> 00:23:55,580
Go check on her quickly.

331
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,620
-Yes.
-Yes.

332
00:25:30,130 --> 00:25:31,020
Mo Xiao!

333
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:33,690
Lixue.

334
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,450
You've already saved the person you wanted to save.

335
00:25:57,450 --> 00:25:58,780
Aren't you leaving yet?

336
00:26:17,470 --> 00:26:18,870
The person I want to save,

337
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:20,710
there's still one more.

338
00:26:21,940 --> 00:26:22,760
Lixue,

339
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:23,900
come with me.

340
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:31,950
We'll meet again.

341
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,560
What if I say I'm not leaving?

342
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:36,380
Lixue, have you forgotten

343
00:26:36,380 --> 00:26:37,860
when we climbed to the peak of Snow Peak,

344
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:38,980
the vision we saw?

345
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,200
As for avenging my father,

346
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,570
I will investigate it myself.

347
00:26:48,570 --> 00:26:50,330
You should quickly leave with your fellow disciples.

348
00:26:50,330 --> 00:26:51,910
Master is an unruly person.

349
00:26:51,930 --> 00:26:53,260
You've destroyed his Love and Desire Valley.

350
00:26:53,260 --> 00:26:54,320
He won't let it go easily.

351
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:54,840
Lixue,

352
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:57,300
I will definitely uncover the truth about this matter.

353
00:26:57,300 --> 00:26:58,430
-Trust me.
-No need.

354
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:01,040
Avenging my father has nothing to do with you.

355
00:27:02,770 --> 00:27:03,450
Lixue.

356
00:27:07,770 --> 00:27:09,300
Do we really have to do this?

357
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:19,610
You are the emotionless sword immortal of the Shushan Sect.

358
00:27:19,610 --> 00:27:22,140
I am the corrupted Star Lord of the Demon Sect.

359
00:27:22,660 --> 00:27:23,750
Between us,

360
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,710
there is no other choice.

361
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:29,120
Emotionless.

362
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,000
I originally

363
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:36,280
believed you.

364
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:39,430
But later I found out

365
00:27:40,010 --> 00:27:41,570
it was all a lie.

366
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:43,560
You deceived me again.

367
00:27:44,860 --> 00:27:47,630
I truly haven't been bewitched by the Love and Desire Poison.

368
00:27:47,630 --> 00:27:49,360
But precisely because of this,

369
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:52,830
every word I've said to you comes from my heart.

370
00:27:53,970 --> 00:27:56,150
If it weren't for the guise of the Love and Desire Poison,

371
00:27:56,150 --> 00:27:59,010
as the Young Sect Leader of the Shushan Sect, these words

372
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:01,010
I fear I would never be able to utter.

373
00:28:03,610 --> 00:28:05,340
I belong to the immortal sects,

374
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:08,060
where the great Way comes first.

375
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:10,210
I have no choice.

376
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,790
But my only true feelings

377
00:28:18,120 --> 00:28:20,310
have fallen into the Crimson Abyss.

378
00:28:31,090 --> 00:28:31,910
Lixue.

379
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:51,780
Zisu.

380
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:53,740
The three of us

381
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:56,220
grew up together with the Young Sect Leader.

382
00:29:57,460 --> 00:29:59,410
As to what are you thinking in your heart,

383
00:29:59,410 --> 00:30:00,540
others may not know,

384
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:03,090
but I understand better than anyone.

385
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:05,170
Actually,

386
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:07,720
you've always been in love with the Young Sect Leader.

387
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:10,650
However, due to sect rules, you couldn't express it.

388
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:13,700
This time, affected by the Love and Desire Poison,

389
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:16,280
you finally dared to reveal your true feelings, right?

390
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:17,080
This time,

391
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:18,810
I've made such a big mistake.

392
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:19,560
Do you think

393
00:30:20,050 --> 00:30:22,820
the Young Sect Leader will expel me from Tiance Villa?

394
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:23,820
Silly girl,

395
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:27,680
there's no right or wrong in liking someone.

396
00:30:28,380 --> 00:30:31,170
The Young Sect Leader is exceptionally talented.

397
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:32,050
In this world,

398
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:34,700
which woman wouldn't like such a man?

399
00:30:35,140 --> 00:30:35,940
Moreover,

400
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:38,430
you two spend time together day and night.

401
00:30:38,610 --> 00:30:41,540
It's understandable to develop feelings over time.

402
00:30:41,770 --> 00:30:42,660
Zifeng,

403
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:45,660
could it be that you also like the Young Sect Leader?

404
00:30:46,100 --> 00:30:48,230
My affection for the Young Sect Leader

405
00:30:48,670 --> 00:30:50,920
has long transcended romantic love.

406
00:30:51,170 --> 00:30:52,250
The Young Sect Leader

407
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:54,280
is the future leader of Shushan Sect,

408
00:30:54,280 --> 00:30:56,010
a leader among immortal sects.

409
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:59,200
He is the person I want to follow for my entire life.

410
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,880
What I want to do in this life

411
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:04,790
is to help him achieve merit for the immortal sects.

412
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,800
This

413
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,640
is enough for me to dedicate my entire life

414
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,900
to strive and improve.

415
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:10,950
Like this,

416
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:12,990
what else could be unsatisfying?

417
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:17,210
We've cultivated together since childhood.

418
00:31:17,210 --> 00:31:19,100
Why is it that you understand everything

419
00:31:19,100 --> 00:31:20,620
more thoroughly than I do?

420
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,710
I come from the Fengyu Branch.

421
00:31:23,740 --> 00:31:26,640
I helped the Young Sect Leader understand all matters under heaven.

422
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:28,640
I naturally have heard and seen more.

423
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:29,770
So,

424
00:31:30,370 --> 00:31:31,660
some things,

425
00:31:32,540 --> 00:31:34,070
I've already seen through.

426
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:35,260
Then, will the Young Sect Leader

427
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,660
really not drive me away?

428
00:31:37,320 --> 00:31:40,500
The Young Sect Leader's cultivation is far above yours and mine.

429
00:31:40,500 --> 00:31:43,030
How could he blame you for such a small matter?

430
00:31:44,970 --> 00:31:45,770
However,

431
00:31:46,620 --> 00:31:47,420
Zisu,

432
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:52,000
the Young Sect Leader's path of cultivation is long and endless.

433
00:31:52,080 --> 00:31:54,880
It's already a blessing that we can accompany him.

434
00:31:55,170 --> 00:31:56,310
Some things

435
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:58,650
will eventually change with time.

436
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,190
So,

437
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,800
what you need to overcome

438
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,730
is the hurdle in your own heart.

439
00:32:05,470 --> 00:32:06,530
Do you understand?

440
00:32:08,420 --> 00:32:09,220
I understand.

441
00:32:11,650 --> 00:32:12,750
Zisu, come back quickly!

442
00:32:12,750 --> 00:32:14,610
The Young Sect Leader is injured.

443
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,260
Young Sect Leader.

444
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,300
Young Sect Leader.

445
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:31,080
How did you get so badly injured?

446
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:32,400
It's all our fault.

447
00:32:32,420 --> 00:32:33,980
We failed to protect you.

448
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:36,940
It's nothing.

449
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:39,190
Just some superficial wounds.

450
00:32:39,190 --> 00:32:40,490
Some ointment will do.

451
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:45,390
You three, please leave.

452
00:32:45,390 --> 00:32:46,680
I need to speak with Mo Xiao.

453
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,400
Yes.

454
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:50,910
Alright, sit down.

455
00:32:51,060 --> 00:32:51,550
Uncle Master.

456
00:32:51,550 --> 00:32:52,290
Sit down.

457
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:53,780
You may go.

458
00:33:00,380 --> 00:33:02,910
Feng Lixue has also escaped with Chongguang?

459
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:03,990
Yes.

460
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:09,840
Before I came here,

461
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:11,610
the Sect Leader repeatedly instructed me

462
00:33:11,610 --> 00:33:12,610
that if I see you,

463
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:13,910
I must tell you

464
00:33:13,930 --> 00:33:16,150
to kill Feng Lixue without fail when you see her.

465
00:33:16,150 --> 00:33:17,950
But you always refuse to do it.

466
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,920
You are clearly capable of doing it.

467
00:33:24,050 --> 00:33:24,960
Uncle Master,

468
00:33:26,020 --> 00:33:29,350
Feng Lixue misunderstood because of what Feng Xingtian did

469
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:33,200
to harm the Sword Sovereign years ago.

470
00:33:33,820 --> 00:33:34,800
Therefore,

471
00:33:35,770 --> 00:33:38,970
she blamed me and the Shushan Sect for her father's death.

472
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:41,120
That's why she was later exploited by Chongguang

473
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,840
and fell into the path of evil.

474
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:44,920
But she wasn't originally evil.

475
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:48,620
She's trapped in the demon's lair because she doesn't know the truth.

476
00:33:48,620 --> 00:33:50,300
She is also a pitiful person.

477
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,880
Although that may be true,

478
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,510
but the Sect Leader...

479
00:33:57,150 --> 00:33:59,360
Come to think of it, it's really strange.

480
00:33:59,360 --> 00:34:02,390
The Sect Leader is usually kind-hearted,

481
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,720
but when it comes to Feng Lixue,

482
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:05,580
he insists that you must kill her.

483
00:34:05,870 --> 00:34:07,730
What could be the reason for this?

484
00:34:08,780 --> 00:34:09,949
Perhaps Master

485
00:34:10,620 --> 00:34:13,000
harbors resentment because of Feng Xingtian's

486
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:14,659
duel with the Sword Sovereign

487
00:34:14,719 --> 00:34:17,130
and the Sword Sovereign's subsequent seclusion,

488
00:34:17,130 --> 00:34:19,060
so he's taking it out on Feng Lixue.

489
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,120
Alright.

490
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:28,219
Since things have come to this point,

491
00:34:28,270 --> 00:34:30,699
when you next see the Sect Leader,

492
00:34:32,870 --> 00:34:35,670
you should explain the situation to him yourself.

493
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,850
Take good care of your wounds.

494
00:34:43,210 --> 00:34:43,850
Master,

495
00:34:44,639 --> 00:34:46,489
I know you want me to kill Lixue

496
00:34:46,510 --> 00:34:48,639
because of the talk of a fatal destiny,

497
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:52,290
but Lixue fell off the cliff years ago because of my mistake.

498
00:34:52,340 --> 00:34:54,270
Ten years later, when we met again,

499
00:34:54,270 --> 00:34:56,940
Lixue even saved my life in a critical moment.

500
00:34:58,350 --> 00:35:01,690
This time, when I went to the Crimson Abyss to find the antidote,

501
00:35:01,690 --> 00:35:03,420
it was also Lixue who helped me.

502
00:35:04,260 --> 00:35:06,760
If there really is such a thing as a fatal destiny,

503
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:09,360
I seem more likely to be Lixue's fatal destiny.

504
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,400
How could I

505
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:15,160
bring myself to kill Lixue, who has helped me multiple times?

506
00:35:15,890 --> 00:35:19,780
Master and the Sword Sovereign have both taught me to care for all living beings.

507
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:22,240
How could I, out of concern for my own safety,

508
00:35:22,790 --> 00:35:24,510
harm an innocent life?

509
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:48,710
Supreme Lord.

510
00:35:48,850 --> 00:35:50,780
Star Lord of Shaohao has returned.

511
00:35:55,500 --> 00:35:56,430
Supreme Lord.

512
00:35:56,690 --> 00:35:59,090
Star Lord of Shaohao requests an audience.

513
00:36:20,090 --> 00:36:21,530
Who let you in?

514
00:36:22,010 --> 00:36:22,960
Supreme Lord.

515
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:25,460
Star Lord of Shaohao requests an audience.

516
00:36:26,110 --> 00:36:27,100
Where is he?

517
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,540
In the front hall.

518
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:32,190
Without my orders,

519
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:34,810
you are not allowed to enter in the future.

520
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,640
I have made a mistake.

521
00:36:57,670 --> 00:36:59,130
Please punish me, Master.

522
00:36:59,610 --> 00:37:00,860
Where is the fault?

523
00:37:01,370 --> 00:37:02,590
I have not noticed it.

524
00:37:02,610 --> 00:37:04,170
Mo Xiao pretended to be poisoned.

525
00:37:04,170 --> 00:37:05,530
I fell for the treacherous plot.

526
00:37:05,530 --> 00:37:07,130
I accidentally revealed the antidote for the Love and Desire Poison

527
00:37:07,130 --> 00:37:08,570
was at the Crimson Abyss.

528
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,420
Please punish me, Master.

529
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,000
Lixue,

530
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,440
you are my

531
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,200
only disciple.

532
00:37:20,640 --> 00:37:22,480
I saved you ten years ago.

533
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,550
and made you my disciple.

534
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:26,040
Do you know why?

535
00:37:26,560 --> 00:37:27,480
I do not know.

536
00:37:28,970 --> 00:37:31,100
Because you have hatred in your heart.

537
00:37:31,120 --> 00:37:32,120
Ruthless enough.

538
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:34,040
You have been lying low for ten years,

539
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:35,320
waiting for the opportunity to take revenge.

540
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:37,450
Patient enough, persevering enough.

