00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:41,900
You surpass countless weak and incompetent people in this world.

542
00:37:43,010 --> 00:37:44,210
Only such a person

543
00:37:44,570 --> 00:37:47,650
will you be worthy of being my disciple.

544
00:37:54,750 --> 00:37:56,310
But now you

545
00:37:57,080 --> 00:37:57,880
have changed.

546
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,320
Your forbearance has turned to weakness,

547
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,620
and your resolve

548
00:38:03,120 --> 00:38:04,160
to hesitation.

549
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,440
Are you still the Feng Lixue

550
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:08,880
I saved ten years ago?

551
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:11,020
In these ten years, I've never asked,

552
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:12,230
Master,

553
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:15,410
how did you know I fell off the cliff

554
00:38:15,650 --> 00:38:17,230
and rescued me back then?

555
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:23,030
Were you also at the peak of Snow Peak at that time?

556
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:29,330
Perhaps

557
00:38:30,010 --> 00:38:31,210
this is

558
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:33,640
the destined fate between us.

559
00:38:33,670 --> 00:38:36,730
Then why didn't you save my father at that time, Master?

560
00:38:39,130 --> 00:38:40,780
Are you blaming me?

561
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:44,640
I wouldn't dare,

562
00:38:44,970 --> 00:38:47,770
it's just that if you had saved my father back then,

563
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:49,830
perhaps I would

564
00:38:50,650 --> 00:38:52,050
suffer a little less now.

565
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:56,360
Your father

566
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,800
initially attacked Shushan Sect

567
00:38:58,800 --> 00:39:00,510
just to save you.

568
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:02,460
If he knew

569
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:04,260
that I had already saved you,

570
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:06,540
he should have died without regrets.

571
00:39:06,780 --> 00:39:07,380
Yes,

572
00:39:09,380 --> 00:39:10,640
Master, you're right.

573
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,600
But if

574
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,640
he knew

575
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,320
that his daughter's

576
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:22,430
desire for revenge

577
00:39:23,490 --> 00:39:24,850
has already wavered.

578
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,200
I wonder

579
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:30,710
how he would feel as a wandering soul beneath Fengdu City.

580
00:39:31,010 --> 00:39:32,270
The desire for revenge

581
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,400
has never wavered.

582
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:37,790
Then, has your loyalty to me

583
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,310
wavered?

584
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:58,350
I, Feng Lixue, am clear about gratitude and grudges.

585
00:39:58,350 --> 00:40:00,150
This life is for two things only:

586
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:01,420
First,

587
00:40:01,890 --> 00:40:03,490
to avenge my father's death.

588
00:40:04,270 --> 00:40:04,870
Second,

589
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:07,000
to repay the debt of saving my life.

590
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:09,330
Master, you have shown me great kindness.

591
00:40:09,490 --> 00:40:10,680
My life

592
00:40:11,090 --> 00:40:12,420
belongs to you, Master.

593
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:23,310
What about your heart?

594
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:27,760
Let's

595
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:30,500
ask your heart.

596
00:40:40,850 --> 00:40:41,810
Lixue,

597
00:40:48,030 --> 00:40:49,500
come with me.

598
00:41:29,410 --> 00:41:30,370
Come.

599
00:41:30,940 --> 00:41:32,440
Let's see

600
00:41:32,770 --> 00:41:35,090
the person you're thinking of.

601
00:41:46,390 --> 00:41:47,430
Mo Xiao.

602
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:48,970
Lixue.

603
00:41:53,520 --> 00:41:54,290
Mo Xiao.

604
00:41:54,490 --> 00:41:55,750
Don't come any closer.

605
00:41:56,060 --> 00:41:56,990
Go away.

606
00:41:58,430 --> 00:41:59,760
Stay back.

607
00:42:00,060 --> 00:42:00,990
Leave.

608
00:42:03,580 --> 00:42:04,580
Go.

609
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:06,670
Mo Xiao.

610
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:12,560
Don't come any closer.

611
00:42:12,900 --> 00:42:13,700
No, Mo Xiao.

612
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:14,830
Stay away.

613
00:42:15,170 --> 00:42:16,320
Mo Xiao.

614
00:42:16,530 --> 00:42:18,590
Go away, Mo Xiao, just go!
